  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What makes this game special?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have you ever wondered how you would react if you, your parents, or your best friend betrayed you? <u><i><strong>VelesScary</strong></i></u> is a game that puts that question to the test.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as a student who’s found a summer job. Over the course of three dark and eerie days, you must survive and uncover the secrets of a disturbing store. The ending will reveal just how observant you were throughout the game. So keep your eyes open… and trust no one—maybe not even yourself. Most importantly, immerse yourself in the game’s chilling atmosphere!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3654050/extras/96c77a1c5b3ef76a38fc481f67aa3cd2.poster.avif?t=1748479190\" width=690 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3654050/extras/96c77a1c5b3ef76a38fc481f67aa3cd2.webm?t=1748479190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3654050/extras/96c77a1c5b3ef76a38fc481f67aa3cd2.mp4?t=1748479190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In short:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lately, you’ve been sleeping poorly. Terrifying nightmares and hallucinations haunt you, and you write them down in a notebook. You feel like Vanya is avoiding you… But is that really true?<br>You decide to get to the bottom of this twisted story. But will you survive?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You won’t just be doing the routine work of a cashier—you’ll interact with townspeople, search for answers, solve puzzles, and open doors hiding terrible secrets. Every action you take shapes the story and determines its ending.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3654050/extras/2bb44a6b0f37ebb05b74de1be56bc1c5.avif?t=1748479190\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3654050/extras_big/2bb44a6b0f37ebb05b74de1be56bc1c5.avif?t=1748479190 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game includes various unexpected scenes and interactive objects!<br>Every corner of this dark and mysterious world hides something unique—from strange items that can influence events, to unexpected encounters with unusual characters whose intentions are far from kind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3654050/extras/3d5e79b9f8c8550e1609c473b56af1a4.avif?t=1748479190\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3654050/extras_big/3d5e79b9f8c8550e1609c473b56af1a4.avif?t=1748479190 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What makes this game special?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have you ever wondered how you would react if you, your parents, or your best friend betrayed you? <u><i><strong>VelesScary</strong></i></u> is a game that puts that question to the test.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as a student who’s found a summer job. Over the course of three dark and eerie days, you must survive and uncover the secrets of a disturbing store. The ending will reveal just how observant you were throughout the game. So keep your eyes open… and trust no one—maybe not even yourself. Most importantly, immerse yourself in the game’s chilling atmosphere!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3654050/extras/96c77a1c5b3ef76a38fc481f67aa3cd2.poster.avif?t=1748479190\" width=690 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3654050/extras/96c77a1c5b3ef76a38fc481f67aa3cd2.webm?t=1748479190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3654050/extras/96c77a1c5b3ef76a38fc481f67aa3cd2.mp4?t=1748479190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In short:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lately, you’ve been sleeping poorly. Terrifying nightmares and hallucinations haunt you, and you write them down in a notebook. You feel like Vanya is avoiding you… But is that really true?<br>You decide to get to the bottom of this twisted story. But will you survive?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You won’t just be doing the routine work of a cashier—you’ll interact with townspeople, search for answers, solve puzzles, and open doors hiding terrible secrets. Every action you take shapes the story and determines its ending.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3654050/extras/2bb44a6b0f37ebb05b74de1be56bc1c5.avif?t=1748479190\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3654050/extras_big/2bb44a6b0f37ebb05b74de1be56bc1c5.avif?t=1748479190 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game includes various unexpected scenes and interactive objects!<br>Every corner of this dark and mysterious world hides something unique—from strange items that can influence events, to unexpected encounters with unusual characters whose intentions are far from kind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3654050/extras/3d5e79b9f8c8550e1609c473b56af1a4.avif?t=1748479190\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3654050/extras_big/3d5e79b9f8c8550e1609c473b56af1a4.avif?t=1748479190 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
